WEBVTT

e0604d5c-0abc-4b85-ac5c-6bfc4b289625-0
00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:19.240
This is my name in Chinese and this is my
name written in English.

1ee1d541-f378-4289-a997-a2ddd5dae62f-0
00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:23.000
This is the English names I choose for
myself.

39de8394-41a4-431d-8b90-99e6279671ca-0
00:00:24.040 --> 00:00:26.320
I think they are all my names.

f3e199c2-4e67-4318-9260-90147ebd7a4a-0
00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:27.440
I like them.

92cccbad-c740-41d7-8395-1c07e4fa64d4-0
00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:29.520
They all represent me.

84253fde-6f05-45cc-a8f4-93c955889fbd-0
00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:36.014
But this,
this is the name of a new year and this

84253fde-6f05-45cc-a8f4-93c955889fbd-1
00:00:36.014 --> 00:00:39.480
is another name in social media.

07e19ca8-7fb5-4460-afba-613c779bb8b6-0
00:00:41.240 --> 00:00:42.920
It is not really its name.

f0ec8414-c829-43c8-b28f-372f5ac578e0-0
00:00:43.640 --> 00:00:46.680
It's part of it, but not all of it.

89b34601-e6c0-4074-8e58-b33f1660355f-0
00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:49.360
And it doesn't mean the same thing.

cdff7804-66e5-4a2b-bb19-c4b984802059-0
00:00:50.680 --> 00:00:56.405
This day we are constantly influenced by
things in social media,

cdff7804-66e5-4a2b-bb19-c4b984802059-1
00:00:56.405 --> 00:00:58.960
whether they are true or not.

9e603e0e-de6c-47cd-9927-492708505950-0
00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:02.080
Maybe people don't really care anymore.

7d213fa7-8cf9-4e67-8a0b-ed01237715fd-0
00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:10.468
We watch out of curiosity or just for the
entertainment and over time we forget how

7d213fa7-8cf9-4e67-8a0b-ed01237715fd-1
00:01:10.468 --> 00:01:12.480
things actually happen.

47353c05-850e-4365-b79f-fe22a4cb1899-0
00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:14.360
We forget everything.

48ca88a2-db67-4766-9bcd-c9550ac1bd61-0
00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:18.200
So does the truth not matter anymore?

d6be70d8-3575-4466-8aed-62f68a998cc2-0
00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:22.400
What happens when the name is changed?

e71ba122-899b-4002-9ebf-a252fc096747-0
00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:24.960
Is it still the same thing?

b9f5ca51-99af-46e7-955d-0b7a797673ca-0
00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:36.745
If one day your name was redefined,
retold,

b9f5ca51-99af-46e7-955d-0b7a797673ca-1
00:01:36.745 --> 00:01:43.400
or replaced by a completely different
story, would it still be you?

50df8878-b694-4ec7-a491-16eba661a8b9-0
00:01:44.760 --> 00:01:50.480
This is a festival, not a label,
not a trend, not something for clicks.

fdc23a8c-65b8-485b-831b-031296806234-0
00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:56.920
This is the Spring Festival.

c3dc2bfd-40af-47cc-b1d2-3ec4befd31d0-0
00:01:58.080 --> 00:02:02.306
It has a history, a family dinner,
Red envelopes,

c3dc2bfd-40af-47cc-b1d2-3ec4befd31d0-1
00:02:02.306 --> 00:02:06.621
staying up through the night, fireworks,
memory,

c3dc2bfd-40af-47cc-b1d2-3ec4befd31d0-2
00:02:06.621 --> 00:02:09.880
repeated generation after generation.

2436ad8f-4a63-4202-83ab-044558ab77e5-0
00:02:10.880 --> 00:02:15.240
But now we are starting to call it
something else.

d71acf79-17b6-4d9d-bdae-0eabf93740e4-0
00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:20.080
We replace it with words that feel easier,
more vague.

6e14c23d-7692-46c8-93cb-9d9738ba1ae2-0
00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:26.840
It doesn't seem like a big difference,
but slowly we forget what it really was.

e1170185-00bf-4d6d-9eed-3ed4bfa7470d-0
00:02:28.840 --> 00:02:33.600
When the culture is renamed it,
it's never just a word that changed.

6a0f4777-28f0-48a1-aea7-efd71f4c6212-0
00:02:34.320 --> 00:02:39.920
It is the history behind it, its origin,
and the memory will carry off it.

d301a89b-f8a1-43a5-b0ac-be553d565ec9-0
00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:47.760
So if one day even we can't remember its
original name, does it still exist?

06524d66-f434-457d-be0c-f09bdc8d68ec-0
00:02:48.520 --> 00:02:52.880
So does the true really not matter
anymore?

b3e30d68-ed20-491a-8dee-4c85d4e85e01-0
00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:56.600
Or have we just gotten used to not asking?

ca47ccc9-1d6a-4f37-97da-d075649c76aa-0
00:02:57.560 --> 00:03:01.197
Maybe the question isn't what others
choose to call it,

ca47ccc9-1d6a-4f37-97da-d075649c76aa-1
00:03:01.197 --> 00:03:04.120
but whether we still remember its real
name.